HEADWORD: Statocracy
<hw>Sta*toc"ra*cy</hw> <pr>(st⟦adot⟧*t⟦ocr⟧k"r⟦adot⟧*s⟦ycr⟧)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>State</ets> + <ets>-cracy</ets>, as in
